            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm mt-8">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">🎯 Pattern Extraction Methodology</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Automated extraction of 600+ high-quality patterns from multiple datasets using data-driven approach.</p>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                        <div class="font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-2">Step 1: Data Processing</div>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                            <li>• Load 53K examples (49K toxic, 4K safe)</li>
                            <li>• Clean: lowercase, remove URLs/mentions</li>
                            <li>• Extract n-grams (1-3 words)</li>
                            <li>• Result: 330K unique toxic n-grams</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                        <div class="font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-2">Step 2: Quality Filtering</div>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                            <li>• Calculate toxicity ratio per pattern</li>
                            <li>• Filter: ratio ≥ 70%, count ≥ 5</li>
                            <li>• Validate against safe corpus</li>
                            <li>• Result: 571 high-quality patterns</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                        <div class="font-semibold text-purple-600 mb-2">Step 3: Integration</div>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                            <li>• Categorize by keywords</li>
                            <li>• Select top 100 per category</li>
                            <li>• Generate regex patterns</li>
                            <li>• Result: 413 production-ready</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">📊 Extraction Results</h4>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600">600+</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">Total Patterns</div>
